Interface GameCommandProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BattleshipCommandProcessor, VotingCommandProcessor

    public interface GameCommandProcessor
    GameCommandProcessor is an interface that represents the system by which commands are chosen to be run for a given game.
    Version:
    1.0, April 2014
    Author:
    Twitch Plays Battleship Group
